                "name": "Burrow",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "An agrawgh can burrow through solid stone at half its normal burrow rate. When traveling using its burrow speed, as a free action an agrawgh can choose whether to leave a tunnel in its wake that is 10 feet tall by 10 feet wide. As long as the agrawgh does not encounter any non-dirt or non-stone substances along its way, it digests dirt and stone with its stomach acids at a rate equal to its burrow movement speed. An agrawgh can\u2019t run or perform combat maneuvers while burrowing. If an agrawgh encounters any creature while burrowing (such as one using <i>meld with stone</i>), it can\u2019t enter that square."
